main event: On August 15, 1967, at approximately 7:55 PM, multiple objects were observed in the sky north of Oshkosh, Wisconsin.
interesting points: Observers reported seeing approximately 9-10 saucer-shaped objects,The objects displayed unusual maneuvers that seemed to contradict known physics,The sighting lasted for about 15 minutes,The objects accelerated rapidly and stopped abruptly,The observers thought the objects might be new aircraft or missiles.
